---
<BaseLayout
  title={pageTitle}
  description={pageDesc}
  canonicalUrl={pageUrl}
  ogImage="https://upcomingbrand.com/og-image.jpg"
  ogImageAlt="Upcoming Brand - vertical-specific WordPress web design across 12 Maryland industries"
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schema)} slot="head" />

  <Navigation />

  <!-- ── HERO ── -->
  <section class="ih-hero">
    <div class="container ih-hero-wrap">

      <!-- LEFT -->
      <div class="ih-hero-left">
        <div class="ih-hero-tags">
          <span class="ih-hero-pill">
            <span class="ih-hero-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            WordPress Specialists &middot; Maryland
          </span>
          <span class="ih-hero-eyebrow mono-xs">12 industry verticals</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="ih-h1">
          <span class="ih-h1-line">Web design built</span>
          <span class="ih-h1-line"><em class="ih-h1-accent">for your industry,</em></span>
          <span class="ih-h1-line ih-h1-italic">not adapted to it.</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="ih-lede">
          Every industry on this page has different schema requirements, compliance constraints, and conversion patterns. We've built enough sites in each vertical to know the pitfalls before you hit them, from <strong>MRPC-compliant law firm copy</strong> to <strong>HIPAA-aware dental forms</strong> to <strong>IDX-integrated real estate sites</strong>.
        </p>

        <div class="ih-ctas">
          <a href="#contact" class="cta-btn">
            Book a discovery call
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
